==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Feather-edge
<hw>Feath"er-edge`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The thin, new growth around the edge of a shell,
of an oyster.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any thin, as on a board or a razor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feather-edged</ent>⟦br⟧
